overview: Smoking in the barracks is a war crime, at least that's how commander Ashton sees it, Pan is now in deep trouble as he knows Ashton won't go easy on him! Pushed down to the floor to do pushups, then on all four to get his ass whipped, the agony the cadet will suffer is just getting started! You'll see some of the most extreme torments My Dirtiest Fantasy has produced to date! Gut-punching, nipple play, ball slapping and more!
title: Hell Hour: Beaten & Abused Cadet
